\c 63 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 63\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyoon Yaadanii Eeggachuu (Faarfannaa Daawit, isa inni yeroo lafa onaa biyya Yihudaa keessa ture faarfatee dha)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ati Waaqayyo koo ti, ani sin barbaada; lubbuun koo akkuma bishaanii si dheebotti, akka lafti bishaan dhabee, gogee dhama of keessaa fixus, foon koo si yaadee in gaggaba;
\m \bd 2\bd* kana irraa kan ka'es aangoo kee fi ulfina kee arguudhaaf iddoo kee isa qulqullaa'aa keessa ijaan sin barbaaddadhe.
\m \bd 3\bd* Gaarummaa kee argachuun, jireenya ani amma jiraadhu irra in wayya, kanaafis arrabni koo si jajata;
\m \bd 4\bd* ani hamman jirutti sin galateeffadha, harka koo ol qabees maqaa kee nan waammadha.
\m \bd 5\bd* Lubbuun koo akka waan ani coomaa fi dhuka nyaadheetti in quufti, afaan koo arraba ililleetiin si jajata.
\m \bd 6\bd* Lafa ciisicha kootti sin yaadadha, yeroon ilaalaa bulus waa'ee kee nan yaada;
\m \bd 7\bd* ati gargaarsa anaaf taateetta, gaaddisa bobaa kee jalattis sagalee gammachuu nan dhageessisa.
\m \bd 8\bd* lubbuun koo sitti in maxxana, harki kee mirgaas qajeelchee ol na qaba.
\m \bd 9\bd* Warri jireenya koo balleessuu barbaadan garuu, boolla lafa jalaa isa gad fagoo keessa lixuuf jiru.
\m \bd 10\bd* Billaa afaan in bu'u, irbaata waangoos in ta'u. 
\m \bd 11\bd* Mootichi garuu Waaqayyotti in gammada, namni maqaa Waaqayyootiin kakatu hundinuu of in jaja; afaan warra sobduu immoo in cuqqaalama.
\b 
